title: IntroScript
---
Handsome invisible old man : Hello ! 
Bob (you) : Hello ?
Bob : Where am I ? I'm so hungry...
Handsome invisible old man : You're hungry ? Do you like biscuits ? 
Bob : Cookies are all my life. Can you give me a cookie ?
Handsome invisible old man : You think it will be that easy ? Go find a cookie yourself ! 
Bob : ... 
Handsome invisible old man : There is a fish-biscuit machine next to me. 
Bob : A what ?
Handsome invisible old man : This is a simple principle : you give fishes, you get biscuits. Try it !
Bob : Can you give me a fish ?
Handsome invisible old man : Don't you think I'm too old for this ? 
Handsome invisible old man : Make an effort, there is a fishing rod at the end of the docks.
Bob : Ok thank you old man ! 
Handsome invisible old man : Wait a minute. 
Handsome invisible old man : Let me share some wisdom with you. 
Handsome invisible old man : You kids can run around as you always to with ZQSD.
Handsome invisible old man : You can jump or dash with space.
Handsome invisible old man : You can interact with stuff with E. But it's a long press. 
Handsome invisible old man : Now go. 

